c: 9
v: 69
t: "[Hi…ďe wa'i] wano …ďen adinoo…ďe on : …ďe laatinoke …ďur…ďe on sa…ótude doole, …ďur…ďe on …óuu…óude jawle e …ďi…ó…ďe. ∆Āe dakmitori [ontuma] e tagu ma…ď…ďe ngu dakmitor…óon ge…ďal mon ngal wano adinoo…ďe on …ďen dakmitornoo ge…ďal ma…ď…ďe ngal, jumpir…óon wano …ďe jumpirnoo. ∆Āen …óon, golle ma…ď…ďe …óen po…ďii(yirbii) aduna e laakara. Ko …ďen …óon woni hayru…ďe(perdube) …ďen"